articles.title: Putin watches on as Eastern European nation passes law favoring Moscow amid violent protests - Fox News
articles.description: Large demonstrations broke out across Georgia as thousands protest a new foreign agent law that many fear will be a tool to crack down on dissent in a country that is looking to join the EU.
